Thanks!

Please share any comments or suggestions you might have on this study below (optional):

rrt_r_2: took the dogs for a run when I didn't want to

rrt_r_1: My wife is the most incredible person in the world. There are innumerable ways she helps me. If I had to pick one, she loves and validates me and makes me feel valued and loved.
rrt_r_2: If I had to pick a second, she believes in me and encourages me to pursue my dreams more than I thought I should and it has always culminated in success thanks to her immaculate judgement.

rrt_u_1: Listen to me complain about work and actually listened
rrt_u_2: Ordered dinner after a long shift so it would be there when I got home
rrt_u_3: Covered me up when I fell asleep on the couch
rrt_u_4: Took the dog out when he got up before I did
rrt_u_5: Picked up wine after a long week
rrt_u_6: Asked me how I was doing
rrt_u_7: Acknowledged how hard I have been working and encouraged me to keep going
rrt_u_9: Picked me up from work when it was raining
rrt_u_10: Told me he loves me and never lets me forget
